---
title: Sweet Potato Sunshine Salad with Crispy Chickpea, Avocado, and Citrus Dressing over Farro
description: With so many nutritious and delicious ingredients on this plate, you’ll be asking “orange you glad I made this for dinner?” We kid, but this recipe really does feature an outstanding array of vibrant foods. There’s cubes of vitamin-A-rich sweet potatoes, handfuls of arugula, protein-packing chickpeas, and a bright citrus dressing that ties it all together. Oh, and a bed of tender, fiber-rich farro to add some ancient grain oomph.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-potato-sunshine-salad-8646ebb3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-potato-sunshine-salad-9156fa0c.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sweet-potato-sunshine-salad-594149313bddb5373b70bd62
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: North America
